* Provides methods to access metrics about an app installed via Incremental
 * @hide

methods.name: public long getMillisSinceOldestPendingRead()
methods.comment: * @return Milliseconds between now and when the oldest pending read happened

methods.name: public long getMillisSinceLastDataLoaderBind()
methods.comment: * @return duration since last data loader binding attempt

methods.name: public long getDataLoaderBindDelayMillis()
methods.comment: * @return delay in milliseconds to retry data loader binding

methods.name: public int getTotalDelayedReads()
methods.comment: * @return total count of delayed reads caused by pending reads

methods.name: public long getTotalDelayedReadsDurationMillis()
methods.comment: * @return total duration in milliseconds of delayed reads

methods.name: public int getLastReadErrorUid()
methods.comment: * @return the uid of the last read error

methods.name: public long getMillisSinceLastReadError()
methods.comment: * @return duration in milliseconds since the last read error

methods.name: public int getLastReadErrorNumber()
methods.comment: * @return the error number of the last read error
